{"id": 1117, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于“消费升级”这件事，你有哪些困扰？", "description": "为了过上品质生活，买买买需要更新换代，但花钱也有很多麻烦。（题图来自：RIIKKA LAAKSO）", "record_count": 1510, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160725150748zqwAvSTRx1mIpa7d.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-26T03:00:02Z", "options": [{"id": 101821, "content": "没钱。。以及为什么要升级？真的有这必要么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658837}, {"id": 97879, "content": "买东西之前必看评测，好麻烦，不看怕买到鸡肋品", "image": null, "praise_count": 324, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 97881, "content": "固定品牌的超市货用得好好的，突然发现自己被鄙视了", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 101820, "content": "大概化妆品和保健品的使用效果是最让人看不懂的玄学了吧…", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679875}, {"id": 101823, "content": "大部分都食之无味弃之可惜。感觉基本款就够用了。比如dyson", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668850}, {"id": 101891, "content": "你看到的东西很多，但是真正满足你的很少，你要去使劲挑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685045}, {"id": 101894, "content": "同类型产品，同一时间出现太多，价格也差不多，从中选择最好的总要对比好几次", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 691427}, {"id": 101897, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679148}, {"id": 101898, "content": "共和国", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679148}, {"id": 101899, "content": "健健康康", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679148}, {"id": 101900, "content": "可口可乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679148}, {"id": 101901, "content": "现在这样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679148}, {"id": 101904, "content": "没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677958}, {"id": 101905, "content": "问题是没钱啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683695}, {"id": 101911, "content": "我没钱啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692298}, {"id": 101912, "content": "喜欢Nexus 然而没有国行、喜欢Z5c，然而没有国行....喜欢HTC10，国行被歧视....在国内买东西很尴尬啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692298}, {"id": 101913, "content": "花大钱买烂东西的多", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692342}, {"id": 101914, "content": "理性接受", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656148}, {"id": 101916, "content": "眼界太高 能力不够", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686065}, {"id": 101925, "content": "不看评论不敢买", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579558}, {"id": 101926, "content": "理性消费，不盲目跟随！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 561327}, {"id": 101933, "content": "精神需求无止尽的高涨 但物质提供停滞不动", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675345}, {"id": 102445, "content": "花钱容易！挣钱难呀！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694630}, {"id": 101935, "content": "选择困难户，买东西都是点兵点将…", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690206}, {"id": 101937, "content": "网红产品并没有多好，只是跟风买的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171786}, {"id": 105521, "content": "八年前就消费升级了，非常清楚所有东西都海淘是神经病。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672607}, {"id": 101939, "content": "广告高于品质", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688658}, {"id": 101940, "content": "喝个星巴克还要排队", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667513}, {"id": 101942, "content": "网购得找各种券，心好累", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680656}, {"id": 101943, "content": "没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224225}, {"id": 101944, "content": "网购的真假难辨啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692529}, {"id": 101951, "content": "为了所谓爱国，好多好多东西买了被受到⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690595}, {"id": 101952, "content": "各种套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663021}, {"id": 101953, "content": "有任何资源方面的需求都可以找我哦！我会尽一切力量来帮大家的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692550}, {"id": 101954, "content": "有些消费品太老态 太古\n比如茶 有没有点有趣的茶品牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660406}, {"id": 101955, "content": "广东资源整合会广东鞋业联合会蒋彬是你事业路上的万金油！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692550}, {"id": 101956, "content": "有些消费品太老态陈旧 比如茶 有没有点好玩儿的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660406}, {"id": 101957, "content": "蒋彬微信电话13049799720", "image": "img/option/option/20160726215519oNlrs8JktjfWCOXv", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692550}, {"id": 101958, "content": "没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682943}, {"id": 101959, "content": "诚信比人民币贬值来的快", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692583}, {"id": 101960, "content": "失去了生活的乐趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673313}, {"id": 101961, "content": "為什麼東西比以往更不耐用。花錢買自己的開心跟全球的垃圾災難。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673822}, {"id": 101963, "content": "越来越关注性价比", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672964}, {"id": 101964, "content": "便宜好用的东西渐渐消失不见了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157411}, {"id": 101966, "content": "京东、洋码头、淘宝要走一遍才敢出手，麻烦！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670012}, {"id": 101968, "content": "主要是个人消费能力和选择权", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124788}, {"id": 101971, "content": "买好的 并尽其使用价值 不要无谓的浪费", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692651}, {"id": 101972, "content": "如果爱情也像消费升级这么简单，这个世界一定更加美好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593560}, {"id": 101973, "content": "再加点钱就能够买xxx了，无限循环...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682460}, {"id": 101974, "content": "用完奥尔滨再也不想用别的水", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623646}]}